flowchart TD
    subgraph 1. Inlet Pipeline Layer
        MIC[Hardware Microphone] --> |AudioStreamer| PCM[16kHz PCM Float32 Audio Buffer]
    end

    subgraph 2. Processing Layer \nThe Brain
        PCM --> |Process 15,600 samples| YAMNET[YAMNet Inference TFLite\n521 Background Categories]
        YAMNET --> |1024D Embeddings| CUSTOM[HearAlert Custom Classifier\nSpecific High-Risk Sounds]
    end

    subgraph 3. Filtration Layer \nThe Rules
        YAMNET --> |Labels & Scores| CONF[Confidence Filtering > 0.45]
        CUSTOM --> |Top Label & Score| CONF
        CONF --> |Valid Sound| THROTTLE[Throttle / Frequency Cap]
        THROTTLE --> |Debounced Event| ZONE[Smart Zone Context Filter\ne.g., 'Street Mode']
    end

    subgraph 4. Outlet Action Layer \nThe Brawn
        ZONE --> |Trigger Verified Event| UI[30FPS Spectrum Analyzer UI Update]
        ZONE --> |Trigger Action| HAPTIC[Vibration Engine specific pattern]
        ZONE --> |Trigger Action| STROBE[Camera LED Flash Strobe]
        ZONE --> |Sync Event| DB[(Remote Event Log)]
    end

    style MIC fill:#eee,stroke:#333
    style PCM fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
    style YAMNET fill:#f9f,stroke:#333
    style CUSTOM fill:#ff9,stroke:#333
    style CONF fill:#dfd,stroke:#333
    style THROTTLE fill:#dfd,stroke:#333
    style ZONE fill:#dfd,stroke:#333
    style UI fill:#eee,stroke:#333
    style HAPTIC fill:#fbb,stroke:#333
    style STROBE fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    style DB fill:#ffb,stroke:#333
